'''Gricha''' were [[Larva/Legends|larval]] creatures used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] to seal holes in their [[grashal]] buildings. Gricha ate sand and secreted a shell-like substance. They were presumably a smaller form of the [[gragricha]].

